# Frontend (React 19 + TypeScript)

## Structure

- Feature code: `frontend/src/features/{module}/`
- Register routes in `frontend/src/app/modules.tsx` (sidebar, breadcrumbs, permissions)
- Import alias: `#/*` → `src/*` — not deep relative paths

## API and state

- HTTP: `api` from `#/lib/api.ts` (ky, cookie auth, CSRF)
- Server state: TanStack Query
- Forms: react-hook-form + zod
- Errors: `describeApiError()` from `#/lib/apiErrors.ts`

## i18n

- No hardcoded user-facing strings on gap screens
- Add keys to `frontend/src/i18n/locales/id/` and `en/` — **Indonesian is default locale**
- Use existing namespaces (`documentStatus.*`, `invoiceStatus.*`, module helpers)

## Shared UI (mandatory for parity)

| Pattern | Components |
|---------|------------|
| Transaction screens | `LegacyTransactionToolbar`, `EditableLineGrid`, `LookupFieldInput`, `LookupDialog` |
| Master CRUD | `CrudPage` |
| Credit/overdue confirms | `runWithBusinessRuleConfirm` from `#/features/common/businessRuleFlow` |

See [docs/modules/shared/ui-foundation/](docs/modules/shared/ui-foundation/).

## Permissions

Gate actions with `useModuleAccess`, `usePermissions` from `#/lib/auth.tsx`.

## Tests

Co-locate `*.test.tsx`; Vitest setup in `frontend/src/test/setup.ts`.
